<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Springbank Hill</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">As of 2006, 93.2% of homes in Springbank Hill are detached single-family homes (bungalow, two-storey homes), with the remaining percentage being lowrise apartments and townhouses, with 3.4% of homes being used as rentals.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">To the east of Springbank Hill is the Westhills Shopping Centre, which has a collection of shops, restaurants and medical facilities (dental and doctor clinics and pharmacies) and a multiplex theatre showing the latest releases.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Family restaurants are easy to come by, with a Montana’s, Moxie’s Grill and Swiss Chalet, as well as a number of fast food restaurants.</p>
        </div>
